xtra.check:
-- 输入参数 prot_buff: 协议包原始字节、pos_begin：校验开始字节位置、pos_end：校验结束字节位置
-- 返回值：返回特定长度字符串
function My_xor8(prot_buff, pos_begin, pos_end)
	local res = 0
	for i=pos_begin, pos_end do
		res = res ~ string.byte(prot_buff, i)
	end
	return string.format("%02X", res) 
end
xtra.pack:
-- 输入参数 seg_name: 协议段名称、seg_value: 协议段值
-- 返回值: 返回打包后的string
function PackFloat_D(seg_name, seg_value)
	local str = string.format("%.5f", seg_value)
	if seg_name=="WD" then  --注：纬度是最后一个字符串，不需要分割符F
		return string.gsub(str, "%.", "D")
	else
		return string.gsub(str, "%.", "D").."F"
	end
end
xtra.unpack:
-- 输入参数 seg_name: 协议段名称、prot_buff：报文原始字节、 pos: 当前解析位置
-- 返回值：必须返回2个值，第1个为解析得到的值，第2个为解析使用的字节长度
function UnpackFloat_D(seg_name, prot_buff, pos)
	local pos_end = pos
	local str = ""
	if seg_name=="WD" then
		pos_end = string.len(prot_buff)
		str = string.sub(prot_buff, pos, pos_end)
	else
		pos_end = string.find(prot_buff, "F", pos)
		str = string.sub(prot_buff, pos, pos_end-1)
	end
	str = string.gsub(str, "D", ".")
	return tonumber(str), pos_end-pos+1
end

content.script:
function entry()
    local answer1 = ask('ok',  {title='提示', msg='确认后继续'})
    print(answer1) ------>'ok'
    delay(10)
    log.info('log_info')
    log.warn("log.warn test")
    log.error("log.error test")
    log.step("log.step test")
    log.action("log.action test") 
    log.doing("doing")
    log.check("check", true)
    log.check("check", false)
	TICK = 10
	for i=1, 100 do
        record.x = i
        record.y = i+math.random(1,20)
        record.a = {z1 = i*2 -math.random(1,20)}
        delay(TICK)
    end
    local msg = message(protocol.prot1)
    msg.wd  = 10.3
    msg.sd = 9
    send(device.dev2.com_1, msg)
    local msg2 = recv(device.dev3.udp1)
    assert(msg2.seg1 == 100)
    record.point.x.z

end

function Stop()
    exit()
end

function SetTick(vars) 
    TICK = vars.tick
    entry()
end

-- 全局变量
STOP = false
STEP = 1
PL = 1
t = 0

--入口函数
function entry(vars, option)
	 while true do
        record.y = 500 * math.sin(2*math.pi*t*PL/1000)
        record.x = t
        t = t + STEP
        delay(STEP)
        if STOP then
            break       
        end
    end
end

 
--停止命令
function Stop()
    STOP = true
end

--设置命令
function Setting(y)
    if y.step and y.step>0 then
        STEP = cmd.step
    end
    if cmd.pl and cmd.pl>0 then
        PL = cmd.pl 
    end
    record.pl = PL
    record.step = STEP
end

--启动命令
function Start(cmd)
    oldstop = STOP
    STOP = false
    if cmd.step and cmd.step>0 then
        STEP = cmd.step
    end
    if cmd.pl and cmd.pl>0 then
        PL = cmd.pl 
    end
    record.pl = PL
    record.step = STEP
    if oldstop then
        entry()
    end
end
